org.smartclean.globalUtility.responseUtil.grids

Class ServiceResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smartclean.globalUtility.responseUtil.grids.ServiceResponse

  • public class ServiceResponse
extends Object
    ServiceResponse class defines the structure of the actual service response for the associated module. It also defines utility methods to hold the data component of the service response in the parsed java object format.
